  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What topics should I follow on Quora? Why?",
  "response": "Choosing topics to follow on Quora depends on your interests, goals, and areas where you seek knowledge or entertainment. Here are some popular and beneficial topics to consider:\n\n1. **Technology and Gadgets**:\n   - Stay updated with the latest trends and innovations in technology.\n   - Explore reviews and recommendations on gadgets and electronic devices.\n   - Learn about advancements in fields like AI, blockchain, cybersecurity, etc.\n\n2. **Health and Fitness**:\n   - Gain insights into healthy living, nutrition, and exercise regimes.\n   - Find answers from medical professionals on various health issues.\n   - Discover tips and advice for mental well-being and self-care.\n\n3. **Personal Finance and Investing**:\n   - Learn strategies for investing in stocks, real estate, and other assets.\n   - Follow advice on budgeting, saving, and handling debt.\n   - Understand economic trends and how they affect personal finances.\n\n4. **Career Advice and Professional Development**:\n   - Get tips on resume building, job interviews, and career progression.\n   - Understand workplace dynamics and leadership skills.\n   - Stay informed about different career paths and industry insights.\n\n5. **Science and Research**:\n   - Explore detailed explanations and discussions on various scientific topics.\n   - Discover recent discoveries and ongoing research across multiple fields.\n   - Engage with experts on complex scientific questions.\n\n6. **Books and Literature**:\n   - Find recommendations and reviews for books across various genres.\n   - Discuss themes, characters, and plots with other literature enthusiasts.\n   - Discover new authors and literary movements.\n\n7. **Travel**:\n   - Gather information on travel destinations, tips, and itineraries.\n   - Read about others' travel experiences and cultural insights.\n   - Plan future trips and adventures with well-informed advice.\n\n8. **History**:\n   - Dive into detailed discussions on historical events, figures, and periods.\n   - Understand the context and impact of various historical moments.\n   - Engage with experts and historians to gain deeper knowledge.\n\n9. **Self-Improvement**:\n   - Learn techniques for personal growth, productivity, and time management.\n   - Discuss strategies for setting and achieving goals.\n   - Explore advice on building better habits and living a fulfilling life.\n\n10. **Entertainment**:\n    - Follow discussions on movies, TV shows, music, and other forms of entertainment.\n    - Get recommendations and reviews from other fans.\n    - Participate in fan theories and debates.\n\n11. **Programming and Software Development**:\n    - Stay updated with the latest in software development, languages, and frameworks.\n    - Get solutions to coding problems and best practices.\n    - Network with fellow developers and share experiences.\n\nBy following these topics, you can tailor your Quora feed to include information that's most relevant and beneficial to you, enhancing both your knowledge and enjoyment of the platform.",
